Body: WEBSITE - WHITEPAPER - FACEBOOK - TWITTER - TELEGRAM -BOUNTY   1APayment is a new platform which will unite the parallel worlds of todayâ€™s payment system with the new crypto world and allows customers to access their cryptocredits for almost all payments.    1APayment is a combination of bank, exchanger, payment platform and transfer service. Through our bank you will receive your own debit creditcard.  With this you are able to pay in almost all shops, whether it is the supermarket on the corner, the gas station or the cinema.   Our payment plattform has a similar structure at the online banking.  â€¢ Banking License - International with headquarter in New Zealand â€¢ Creditcard - Pay all with your cryptos! â€¢ Invoice Payment - 3 easy steps for all purposes â€¢ 1to1 Coin - 1 1to1Coin = 1 USDollar with full transparency.     Invoice Payment Service  You can pay the phone bill, the rent or the new car with Bitcoins.  In three simple steps, invoices can be paid with Bitcoins.  Fill the form with the required data Upload the invoice or contract to be paid for Send the bitcoins to the wallet address we provide you.  After we have received the Bitcoins, we will execute the transfer after having 3 blockchain confirmations and send the executed transfer voucher by email as confirmation of the transfer.  Should any questions arise during the processing, our live support team will be happy to help and advise you.  Up to an amount of 1500 Euro per invoice, each invoice payment is made without verification. Invoices over 1500 Euro can be paid with verification.   Legal form   First of all, we create the appropriate legal background Â­ and thus a longÂ­term security. The founding of the 1APayment company is in its last stages and will be completed in the next few days. Through an international New Zealand banking license, it is also legally and tax law feasible. The registration of the company took place in Switzerland. Through different subsidiaries in the individual continents and countries, we will deal with the local conditions. The operators of Masternodes receive rewards for maintaining the network for the coins they hold. The rewards are based on the availability of a node in the decentralized chain network. 500 1AP Coins are required to operate with a masternode. A Masternode owner is entitled to vote on future development proposals. Each transaction requires a minimum of 50 confirmations. The proceeds from the ICO will be used for marketing, credit card integration and the operation of 1AP on trading platforms. The remainder is reserved for the liquidity pool, bonus programs and recommendations.   Â­Unsold coins are transferred to the ICO. Advanced token won't be offered in the ICO phase.
